                                            <button class="bg-transparent border-0 w-100 text-start accordion-button collapsed" type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-item-6" style="overflow-anchor: none;"><span class="accordion-num"> 08</span><span class="accordion-title">Нужно ли добавлять спортивные нагрузки для получения результата?</span><span class="accordion-arrow">
                              <svg class="text-primary svg-inline--fa fa-chevron-down fa-w-14" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" data-prefix="fas" data-icon="chevron-down" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512">
